<font color="#ffff00">Karena dia sudah bangun,</font>

189
00:13:01,416 --> 00:13:02,749
<font color="#ffff00">kami akan pergi.</font>

190
00:13:09,749 --> 00:13:11,916
<font color="#ffff00">Satu hal lagi.</font>

191
00:13:12,874 --> 00:13:14,791
<font color="#ffff00">Beberapa orang belum menyerahkan diri.</font>

192
00:13:15,249 --> 00:13:16,416
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka menghilang.</font>

193
00:13:17,457 --> 00:13:18,541
<font color="#ffff00">Berhati-hatilah.</font>

194
00:13:19,749 --> 00:13:21,499
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka tidak terduga.</font>

195
00:13:34,499 --> 00:13:35,499
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu, Pak Agawa...</font>

196
00:13:36,332 --> 00:13:38,332
<font color="#ffff00">Daigo, apa yang kau lakukan?</font>

197
00:13:38,416 --> 00:13:39,957
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak bisa diam di sini.</font>

198
00:13:40,041 --> 00:13:41,041
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

199
00:13:43,499 --> 00:13:45,499
<font color="#ffff00">Mereka dalam perlindungan polisi, bukan?</font>

200
00:13:46,291 --> 00:13:47,499
<font color="#ffff00">Ya, tentu saja.</font>

201
00:13:47,916 --> 00:13:50,197
<font color="#ffff00">Kita harus ke kantor polisi
untuk mengambil barang mereka.</font>

202
00:13:50,791 --> 00:13:51,791
<font color="#ffff00">Tunggu...</font>

203
00:13:54,457 --> 00:13:55,707
<font color="#ffff00">Ponselku...</font>

204
00:14:00,166 --> 00:14:02,624
<font color="#ffff00">Ponselmu sudah tidak ada
sejak kami menemukanmu.</font>

205
00:14:03,416 --> 00:14:05,416
<font color="#ffff00">Kami juga tidak menemukannya di sungai.</font>

206
00:14:05,666 --> 00:14:07,666
<font color="#ffff00">- Benar, 'kan?
- Benar.</font>

207
00:14:08,582 --> 00:14:09,582
<font color="#ffff00">Begitu rupanya.</font>

208
00:14:09,666 --> 00:14:10,666
<font color="#ffff00">Baiklah.</font>

209
00:14:11,082 --> 00:14:12,082
<font color="#ffff00">Hei...</font>

210
00:14:12,374 --> 00:14:13,374
<font color="#ffff00">Apa maksudmu barang kami?</font>

211
00:14:14,082 --> 00:14:15,207
<font color="#ffff00">Kau mau ke mana?</font>

212
00:14:17,374 --> 00:14:19,249
<font color="#ffff00">Pergi menangkap mereka
yang melarikan diri.</font>

213
00:14:19,332 --> 00:14:20,416
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan lakukan itu.</font>

214
00:14:20,624 --> 00:14:21,984
<font color="#ffff00">Kau baru saja mendapat 13 jahitan.</font>

215
00:14:23,332 --> 00:14:24,499
<font color="#ffff00">Aku baik-baik saja.</font>

216
00:14:24,582 --> 00:14:26,041
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak baik-baik saja.</font>

217
00:14:26,541 --> 00:14:27,624
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo, mari kita pergi.</font>

218
00:14:33,832 --> 00:14:35,249
<font color="#ffff00">Dengarkan aku sesekali!</font>

219
00:14:45,499 --> 00:14:46,666
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Aku Nakamura.</i></font>

220
00:14:47,624 --> 00:14:48,624
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Petugas Agawa?</i></font>

221
00:14:48,707 --> 00:14:50,457
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mengenai jari yang tempo lalu...</i></font>

222
00:14:51,249 --> 00:14:52,999
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kami mengetahui pemilik jari tersebut.</i></font>

223
00:14:54,332 --> 00:14:59,916
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Itu jari milik pendahulumu
yang menghilang...</i></font>

224
00:15:01,707 --> 00:15:04,416
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Itu jari milik Pak Osamu Kano.</i></font>

225
00:15:06,916 --> 00:15:08,041
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Selain itu...</i></font>

226
00:15:09,207 --> 00:15:12,374
<font color="#ffff00"><i>zat yang cocok dengan air liur manusia</i></font>

227
00:15:12,457 --> 00:15:14,124
<font color="#ffff00"><i>ditemukan pada jari tersebut.</i></font>

228
00:15:15,166 --> 00:15:16,166
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ini berarti...</i></font>

229
00:15:18,499 --> 00:15:21,499
<font color="#ffff00"><i>jari itu mungkin digigit putus
oleh seseorang.</i></font>

230
00:15:23,582 --> 00:15:24,999
<font color="#ffff00">Ini gawat.</font>

231
00:15:25,499 --> 00:15:26,832
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang harus kita lakukan?</font>

232
00:15:27,374 --> 00:15:28,791
<font color="#ffff00">Serahkan padaku.</font>

233
00:15:49,832 --> 00:15:56,416
<font color="#ffff00">AGAWA: AKU INGIN BERBICARA LANGSUNG.
KAPAN SEKIRANYA KAU MEMILIKI WAKTU?</font>

234
00:16:17,749 --> 00:16:18,749
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

235
00:16:19,082 --> 00:16:20,332
<font color="#ffff00">Ada yang datang.</font>

236
00:16:40,832 --> 00:16:41,999
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa kau ada di sini?</font>

237
00:16:46,666 --> 00:16:48,499
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan-jangan lukamu itu...</font>

238
00:16:48,582 --> 00:16:49,582
<font color="#ffff00">Ya...</font>

239
00:16:51,374 --> 00:16:53,874
<font color="#ffff00">Aku terluka saat menanyakan beberapa hal
pada keluarga Goto.</font>

240
00:16:55,124 --> 00:16:56,207
<font color="#ffff00">Maafkan aku.</font>

241
00:16:56,749 --> 00:16:58,166
<font color="#ffff00">Semua karena perkataanku.</font>

242
00:16:58,749 --> 00:16:59,749
<font color="#ffff00">Tidak apa-apa.</font>

243
00:17:00,457 --> 00:17:01,957
<font color="#ffff00">Berkatmu, aku jadi tahu.</font>

244
00:17:02,874 --> 00:17:05,041
<font color="#ffff00">Keluarga Goto
memang menyembunyikan sesuatu.</font>

245
00:17:08,749 --> 00:17:10,749
<font color="#ffff00">Pak Kano mungkin tertangkap oleh mereka.</font>

246
00:17:17,624 --> 00:17:19,374
<font color="#ffff00">Apakah kau akan
melanjutkan penyelidikanmu?</font>

247
00:17:19,624 --> 00:17:21,184
<font color="#ffff00">Meskipun hal seperti itu sudah terjadi?</font>

248
00:17:22,582 --> 00:17:23,916
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak akan berhenti.</font>

249
00:17:28,499 --> 00:17:29,582
<font color="#ffff00">Aku ingat.</font>

250
00:17:33,749 --> 00:17:34,749
<font color="#ffff00">Lihatlah ini.</font>

251
00:17:35,707 --> 00:17:37,541
<font color="#ffff00">Ini riwayat panggilan di ponsel ayahku.</font>

252
00:17:47,916 --> 00:17:48,916
<font color="#ffff00">Apa ini?</font>

253
00:17:49,499 --> 00:17:51,041
<font color="#ffff00">Nomor yang aneh, bukan?</font>

254
00:17:52,999 --> 00:17:54,499
<font color="#ffff00">Itu telepon satelit.</font>

255
00:17:56,624 --> 00:17:58,707
<font color="#ffff00">Panggilan masuk terakhir ke ponsel ayahku.</font>

256
00:18:00,582 --> 00:18:03,249
<font color="#ffff00">Aku sudah mencoba meneleponnya,
tapi tak ada yang menjawab.</font>

257
00:18:04,999 --> 00:18:07,207
<font color="#ffff00">Polisi bisa menyelidikinya, bukan?</font>

258
00:18:08,249 --> 00:18:09,249
<font color="#ffff00">Ini sangat membantu.</font>

259
00:18:16,332 --> 00:18:17,416
<font color="#ffff00">Aku...</font>

260
00:18:20,749 --> 00:18:22,749
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak tahu apa pun tentang ayahku.</font>

261
00:18:26,666 --> 00:18:28,499
<font color="#ffff00">Ayah berlaku aneh...</font>

262
00:18:30,582 --> 00:18:31,582
<font color="#ffff00">Aku menjadi takut...</font>

263
00:18:33,832 --> 00:18:35,832
<font color="#ffff00">dan aku tidak bisa kembali ke sini.</font>

264
00:18:47,832 --> 00:18:48,999
<font color="#ffff00">Tolong berhati-hatilah.</font>

265
00:18:52,166 --> 00:18:54,291
<font color="#ffff00">Aku harap kau tidak kehilangan apa pun.</font>

266
00:18:55,457 --> 00:18:56,457
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

267
00:19:00,541 --> 00:19:02,541
<font color="#ffff00">KANTOR POLISI KUGE</font>

268
00:19:05,041 --> 00:19:07,166
<font color="#ffff00">Anggota keluarga Goto memang gila...</font>

269
00:19:09,166 --> 00:19:10,916
<font color="#ffff00">tapi Keisuke berbeda.</font>

270
00:19:26,999 --> 00:19:27,999
<font color="#ffff00">Ayo berangkat.</font>

271
00:19:29,749 --> 00:19:31,166
<font color="#ffff00">Kau harus jelaskan padaku.</font>

272
00:19:32,416 --> 00:19:33,416
<font color="#ffff00">Oh...</font>

273
00:19:34,624 --> 00:19:36,499
<font color="#ffff00">Dia adalah anak perempuan Pak Kano.</font>

274
00:19:36,957 --> 00:19:38,957
<font color="#ffff00">- Dia membantuku...
- Bukan itu maksudku.</font>

275
00:19:40,041 --> 00:19:42,041
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak lihat ini semua terlalu aneh?</font>

276
00:19:43,124 --> 00:19:45,124
<font color="#ffff00">Pendahulumu menghilang.</font>

277
00:19:45,541 --> 00:19:46,999
<font color="#ffff00">Kau nyaris mati.</font>

278
00:19:47,166 --> 00:19:48,999
<font color="#ffff00">Namun, kau akan
melanjutkan penyelidikanmu?</font>

279
00:19:49,832 --> 00:19:51,666
<font color="#ffff00">Kenapa harus kau yang pergi?</font>

280
00:19:55,041 --> 00:19:57,624
<font color="#ffff00">Pikirkan perasaan orang yang menunggumu.</font>

281
00:19:58,082 --> 00:20:00,041
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tahu seberapa khawatirnya aku?</font>

282
00:20:01,999 --> 00:20:02,832
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf...</font>

283
00:20:02,916 --> 00:20:04,041
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tidak butuh maaf.</font>

284
00:20:05,541 --> 00:20:07,999
<font color="#ffff00">Jika merasa terancam lagi,
aku akan pergi bersama Mashiro.</font>

285
00:20:14,624 --> 00:20:15,791
<font color="#ffff00">Usul yang bagus.</font>

286
00:20:17,166 --> 00:20:18,207
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

287
00:20:20,124 --> 00:20:21,416
<font color="#ffff00">Apa kau serius?</font>

288
00:20:21,999 --> 00:20:24,249
<font color="#ffff00">Kau juga anggota keluarga. Berengsek!</font>

289
00:20:24,332 --> 00:20:25,874
<font color="#ffff00">Yuki!</font>

290
00:20:29,249 --> 00:20:30,916
<font color="#ffff00">Ada yang belum kuberi tahu padamu.</font>

291
00:20:31,416 --> 00:20:32,416
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

292
00:20:33,541 --> 00:20:35,082
<font color="#ffff00">Ingat saat kita baru pindah</font>

293
00:20:35,666 --> 00:20:37,166
<font color="#ffff00">dan Mashiro pergi menghilang?</font>

294
00:20:39,249 --> 00:20:40,457
<font color="#ffff00">Dia memberiku...</font>

295
00:20:41,832 --> 00:20:43,916
<font color="#ffff00">potongan jari manusia.</font>

296
00:20:52,374 --> 00:20:56,374
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Saat itu aku mengira itu milik Gin Goto
yang meninggal dimakan beruang.</i></font>

297
00:20:56,957 --> 00:20:58,374
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Namun, saat kuselidiki, aku salah.</i></font>

298
00:21:01,707 --> 00:21:02,707
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Aku menduga...</i></font>

299
00:21:04,957 --> 00:21:07,957
<font color="#ffff00"><i>jari itu milik pendahuluku yang hilang,
Pak Kano.</i></font>

300
00:21:11,416 --> 00:21:12,666
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Tempat ini terlalu berbahaya.</i></font>

301
00:21:12,749 --> 00:21:14,166
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Kalian berdua harus pergi.</i></font>

302
00:21:15,332 --> 00:21:16,999
<font color="#ffff00">SELAMAT DATANG DI DESA KUGE</font>

303
00:21:40,957 --> 00:21:41,957
<font color="#ffff00">Agawa.</font>

304
00:21:42,999 --> 00:21:43,999
<font color="#ffff00">Pak Kepala.</font>

305
00:21:44,749 --> 00:21:46,166
<font color="#ffff00">Bagaimana lukamu?</font>

306
00:21:47,124 --> 00:21:49,207
<font color="#ffff00">Kantor ini ramai dengan cerita tentangmu.</font>

307
00:21:51,041 --> 00:21:52,791
<font color="#ffff00">- Bawa keluarganya ke dalam.
- Baik.</font>

308
00:22:01,541 --> 00:22:03,707
<font color="#ffff00">Semuanya mau bertemu denganmu.</font>

309
00:22:06,582 --> 00:22:09,416
<font color="#ffff00">Reputasimu bahkan telah sampai
ke kota kecil seperti ini.</font>

310
00:22:11,416 --> 00:22:12,999
<font color="#ffff00">Kami dengar kau detektif yang hebat.</font>

311
00:22:14,249 --> 00:22:15,249
<font color="#ffff00">Pak Kepala,</font>

312
00:22:15,707 --> 00:22:17,124
<font color="#ffff00">bisakah kita bicara sebentar?</font>

313
00:22:17,957 --> 00:22:18,957
<font color="#ffff00">Tentu.</font>

314
00:22:19,541 --> 00:22:20,624
<font color="#ffff00">Apakah kau...</font>

315
00:22:21,749 --> 00:22:23,249
<font color="#ffff00">- Ya.
- Kalau begitu, mari.</font>

316
00:22:27,457 --> 00:22:29,374
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Mengenai pendahuluku, Pak Kano,</i></font>

317
00:22:29,457 --> 00:22:31,999
<font color="#ffff00">apakah Bapak tahu bahwa dia menghilang</font>

318
00:22:32,416 --> 00:22:34,416
<font color="#ffff00">setelah bertemu dengan Keluarga Goto?</font>

319
00:22:35,166 --> 00:22:37,166
<font color="#ffff00">Apa? Apa maksudmu?</font>

320
00:22:37,416 --> 00:22:39,166
<font color="#ffff00">Aku hanya dengar dia menghilang.</font>

321
00:22:41,499 --> 00:22:42,499
<font color="#ffff00">Aku pikir</font>

322
00:22:43,207 --> 00:22:47,374
<font color="#ffff00">dia ditangkap oleh Keluarga Goto.</font>

323
00:22:48,957 --> 00:22:49,957
<font color="#ffff00">Atau...</font>

324
00:22:51,374 --> 00:22:52,707
<font color="#ffff00">mereka sudah membunuhnya.</font>

325
00:22:59,916 --> 00:23:01,249
<font color="#ffff00">Apakah kau memiliki bukti?</font>

326
00:23:04,124 --> 00:23:06,874
<font color="#ffff00">Itu alasanmu pergi menemui mereka?
Untuk menyelidiki hal tersebut?</font>

327
00:23:07,416 --> 00:23:08,416
<font color="#ffff00">Ya.</font>

328
00:23:09,457 --> 00:23:11,874
<font color="#ffff00">Dan mereka menyerangku.</font>

329
00:23:26,457 --> 00:23:28,041
<font color="#ffff00">Apakah itu tanpa provokasi?</font>

330
00:23:30,291 --> 00:23:31,291
<font color="#ffff00">Maaf?</font>

331
00:23:32,291 --> 00:23:35,707
<font color="#ffff00">Kau yakin kau tidak berbuat kasar
pada mereka terlebih dulu?</font>

332
00:23:36,999 --> 00:23:41,874
<font color="#ffff00">Lagi pula kau memiliki insiden
dalam riwayatmu.</font>

333
00:23:42,999 --> 00:23:45,124
<font color="#ffff00">Selain itu, Kano mengajukan
pengunduran diri, bukan?</font>

334
00:23:45,207 --> 00:23:46,416
<font color="#ffff00">Ya. Kurasa begitu.</font>

335
00:23:46,499 --> 00:23:47,916
<font color="#ffff00">- Meski begitu...
- Intinya,</font>

336
00:23:48,499 --> 00:23:51,832
<font color="#ffff00">jangan mengusik singa yang tertidur.</font>

337
00:23:58,374 --> 00:24:00,457
<font color="#ffff00">Jangan sentuh Keluarga Goto.</font>

338
00:24:03,832 --> 00:24:06,082
<font color="#ffff00">Aku lahir dan besar di Desa Kuge.</font>

339
00:24:07,374 --> 00:24:09,624
<font color="#ffff00">Orang tuaku selalu mengatakan itu padaku.</font>

340
00:24:10,749 --> 00:24:14,082
<font color="#ffff00">Jadi, aku tahu seperti apa Keluarga Goto.</font>

341
00:24:24,124 --> 00:24:25,457
<font color="#ffff00">- Yamamoto.
- Ya?</font>

342
00:24:25,707 --> 00:24:27,082
<font color="#ffff00">Panggil Kepala Divisi Kriminal.</font>

343
00:24:27,166 --> 00:24:29,499
<font color="#ffff00">Mari selidiki ulang kasus Pak Kano.</font>

344
00:24:29,832 --> 00:24:31,041
<font color="#ffff00">- Baik.
- Seki,</font>

345
00:24:31,541 --> 00:24:35,624
<font color="#ffff00">coba cek kembali
mengenai pengunduran dirinya.</font>

346
00:24:35,707 --> 00:24:36,707
<font color="#ffff00">Baik, Pak.</font>

347
00:24:39,749 --> 00:24:41,666
<font color="#ffff00">Terima kasih, Pak.</font>

348
00:24:41,874 --> 00:24:42,874
<font color="#ffff00">Sama-sama.</font>

349
00:24:46,332 --> 00:24:47,332
<font color="#ffff00">Namun...</font>

350
00:24:47,832 --> 00:24:50,166
<font color="#ffff00">kau tidak boleh mengerjakan kasus ini.</font>

351
00:24:51,624 --> 00:24:52,874
<font color="#ffff00">Apa? Tunggu dulu...</font>

352
00:24:53,207 --> 00:24:55,541
<font color="#ffff00">Kali ini kau adalah korban.</font>

353
00:24:56,124 --> 00:24:58,416
<font color="#ffff00">Kau tidak boleh terlibat.
Ini protokol standar.</font>

354
00:25:00,207 --> 00:25:01,416
<font color="#ffff00">Selain itu...</font>

355
00:25:02,041 --> 00:25:03,749
<font color="#ffff00">keluargamu pasti sangat khawatir padamu.</font>

356
00:25:05,416 --> 00:25:07,707
<font color="#ffff00">Temanilah mereka untuk sekarang.</font>

357
00:25:12,749 --> 00:25:13,749
<font color="#ffff00">Petugas Agawa?</font>

358
00:25:17,082 --> 00:25:19,374
<font color="#ffff00">Ada telepon masuk ke kantor polisi
dari Pak Nakamura</font>

359
00:25:19,457 --> 00:25:20,874
<font color="#ffff00">dari Rumah Sakit Pusat.</font>

360
00:25:22,416 --> 00:25:24,249
<font color="#ffff00">Terima kasih. Aku undur diri dahulu.</font>

361
00:25:24,332 --> 00:25:25,332
<font color="#ffff00">Silakan.</font>

362
00:25:36,332 --> 00:25:38,499
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Ya, aku sudah dengar.</i></font>

363
00:25:39,582 --> 00:25:40,749
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Pasti gawat sekali.</i></font>

364
00:25:42,332 --> 00:25:43,499
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Jadi...</i></font>

365
00:25:44,166 --> 00:25:45,957
<font color="#ffff00"><i>tentang jari itu...</i></font>

366
00:25:47,457 --> 00:25:48,697
<font color="#ffff00">Apakah kau mendapatkan sesuatu?</font>

367
00:25:53,249 --> 00:25:55,166
<font color="#ffff00">Aku ingin berbicara langsung denganmu.</font>

368
00:25:55,916 --> 00:25:58,249
<font color="#ffff00">Bisakah kau datang langsung
ke rumah sakit?</font>

369
00:26:00,291 --> 00:26:01,291
<font color="#ffff00">Ya, tentu saja.</font>

370
00:26:01,916 --> 00:26:02,916
<font color="#ffff00">Aku akan segera ke sana.</font>

371
00:26:03,999 --> 00:26:05,124
<font color="#ffff00">Terima kasih.</font>

372
00:26:05,999 --> 00:26:06,999
<font color="#ffff00">Akan kutunggu.</font>

373
00:26:07,916 --> 00:26:08,916
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Baik.</i></font>

374
00:26:09,041 --> 00:26:10,041
<font color="#ffff00"><i>Sampai nanti.</i></font>

